text: Anticipation II is a mixtape by American singer Trey Songz, released on November 1, 2011, along with the mixtape #LemmeHolDatBeat2 on the same day. On April 24, 2020, Trey Songz re-released the mixtape on streaming platforms, with the original mixtape in the series Anticipation. ==Background== In 2012, the mixtape was supported with The Anticipation 2our with 19 shows in North America. ==Track listing == ==References== Category:2011 albums Category:Trey Songz albums
title: Anticipation II
